################################################################################
# Ultimate++ 2025.1.1 - Comprehensive Cocoa macOS 10.6 Compatibility Patch
################################################################################
#
# Purpose: Full compatibility with macOS 10.6 SDK and gcc 14 compiler
#
# Target Environment:
#   - macOS 10.6 Snow Leopard  
#   - GCC 14 (or legacy GCC 4.2.1)
#   - PowerPC architecture (32/64-bit, big-endian)
#   - Mac OS X 10.6 SDK
#   - No Apple blocks, no ObjC generics, no ARC, no fast enumeration
#
# Files Modified (14 total):
#   Core (1 file):
#   1. uppsrc/Core/ValueUtil.h         - Fixed 'id' keyword conflict
#   
#   CtrlLib (3 files):
#   2. uppsrc/CtrlLib/ChCocoMM.mm      - CGColor conversion, CGRect/NSRect, properties
#   3. uppsrc/CtrlLib/Cocoa.mm         - NSURL API fix, property syntax
#   4. uppsrc/CtrlLib/MacMenu.mm       - Property syntax, SDK defines
#   
#   CtrlCore (8 files):
#   5. uppsrc/CtrlCore/CocoMM.h        - SDK compatibility defines
#   6. uppsrc/CtrlCore/CocoApp.mm      - Removed modern features, for...in loops
#   7. uppsrc/CtrlCore/CocoWin.mm      - Property syntax, type conversions
#   8. uppsrc/CtrlCore/CocoDrawOp.mm   - CGFloat arrays
#   9. uppsrc/CtrlCore/CocoImage.mm    - __bridge cast removal
#  10. uppsrc/CtrlCore/CocoDraw.mm     - NSRect conversion (NSRectFromCGRect)
#  11. uppsrc/CtrlCore/CocoProc.mm     - for...in loops, NSRect conversions
#  12. uppsrc/CtrlCore/CocoClip.mm     - GCC ICE workaround (reduced optimization)
#
#   Draw (1 file):
#  13. uppsrc/Draw/FontCoco.mm         - CoreText orientation constant
#
# Key Changes:
#   ✓ Renamed Upp::Id member variable 'id' → 'v' (fixes keyword conflict)
#   ✓ Added NSColorToCGColor() helper (CGColor property added in 10.8)
#   ✓ Added SDK compatibility defines for all renamed constants
#   ✓ Converted 6 Objective-C fast enumeration loops to traditional C loops
#   ✓ Fixed NSURL fileSystemRepresentation API for 10.6
#   ✓ Converted 40+ property dot notations to message syntax
#   ✓ Fixed CGRect/NSRect/CGSize/NSSize type conversions (use Foundation functions)
#   ✓ Fixed CGFloat vs double array types
#   ✓ Added kCTFontOrientationHorizontal compatibility define
#   ✓ Removed dark mode listeners and Retina/UHD detection
#   ✓ Removed Apple blocks from event monitors
#   ✓ Removed __bridge ARC cast
#   ✓ Added Carbon macro undefs (check, verify, require)
#   ✓ GCC ICE workaround in CocoClip.mm (reduced optimization level)
#
# Statistics:
#   - 14 files changed
#   - 150 lines removed (-)
#   - 228 lines added (+)
#   - Net change: +78 lines
#
# How to Apply:
#   From Ultimate++ v2025.1.1 source directory:
#   $ patch -p1 < patch-cocoa2-10.6-complete.diff
#
# For MacPorts:
#   patchfiles \
#       patch-cocoa2-10.6-complete.diff
#
# Notes:
#   - GCC ICE workaround: If CocoClip.mm still fails with internal compiler
#     error, add to Portfile: configure.cxxflags-append "-fno-exceptions" 
#     for just that file, or reduce to -O0
